{"tid":1086962,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"［2019DSE首戰］中文科討論區［2］","createTime":"2019-04-01T05:31:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-01T05:35:46.000Z","uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bff7bd22e94a61222bc5c1b313d23b65ce867ada","tid":1086962,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:31:30.000Z","msg":"卷四Tips 傳送門<br />\n&lrm;［2019DSE］中文科口試討論及直播區 2 (已整合各有心巴絲tips)<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1059629\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1059629</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n大家可以一齊討論吓點準備卷一到卷三<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔好報咩考前精讀 買咩筆記 補習佬臨尾昆水<br />\n慳啲錢同時間 溫返自己唔識嘅地方 <br />\n有咩唔明可以喺度問 會有好多巴絲幫手解答<br />\n<br />\n希望考之前再幫到多啲同學仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連登有愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我晏啲會post返一啲之前打落嘅tips <br />\n比大家參考返可以點準備<br />\n無必勝嘅策略 只有不服輸嘅心態<br />\n唔好比恐懼擊倒自己<br />\n特別係唔使盲目相信人哋有特別技巧或者例子 <br />\n咩tip中聽完就算 當講笑 <br />\n清楚明白要準備啲咩 足夠就可以了<br />\n雖然讀書唔係兩星期可以大幅改變到嘅嘢<br />\n但係兩星期你集中的話 結果亦可以改寫<br />\n唔好放棄<br />\n前方就是大學之路<br />\n18年學習生涯 就係為咗踏上呢個舞台<br />\n唔好比自己後悔 搏到盡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />德巴字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8f3854f37e77c0407c7aa69e22ffd597fefd26b","tid":1086962,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"我又開咗個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理另外一個，沉口左佢plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8240e260e4b7fe2c83c774e05d48120c6071b5","tid":1086962,"uid":52155,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b8f3854f37e77c0407c7aa69e22ffd597fefd26b","tid":1086962,"uid":208837,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:33:30.000Z","msg":"我又開咗個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />唔好理另外一個，沉口左佢plz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-01T05:35:46.000Z","msg":"你嗰個好好似多啲人覆，沉咗呢個佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}